name: They Will Be No Match For You
Lore: '''At last we will reveal ourselves to the Jedi.''',
Text: 'Deploy on table. When Maul initiates a duel, Hunt Down And Destroy The Jedi (or Their Fire Has Gone Out Of The Universe) is not placed out of play. While armed with a lightsaber, Maul''s duel destiny draws are each +1. (Immune to Alter.)',
